1056
01:06:39,371 --> 01:06:45,084
on how you spent
a weekend with an asshole
from Hollywood for your art.

1057
01:06:45,585 --> 01:06:47,419
KAUFMAN:
I am pathetic. I am a loser.

1058
01:06:47,587 --> 01:06:51,048
So, what is the substance
