to save somebody.

1091
01:08:40,533 --> 01:08:43,911
Every day, someone somewhere
takes a conscious decision

1092
01:08:44,120 --> 01:08:46,538
to destroy someone else.

1093
01:08:46,748 --> 01:08:48,999
